name: Dimensional Fluids #01
description: Life is complicated, and so is art. In this piece, a digitally enhanced photograph of my pour paintings is used as both texture and color to create a new form that feels falsely organic. -- Image displayed 11.9.19 in LA @ InnerSpace Gallery in the CryptoArt show hosted by @MaxOsiris with many other wonderful crypto space artists included. This piece will be sold after the show completes.
